{"履修期": "秋学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "1. To develop students’ English proficiency through the study of academic topics in the field of sociology.2. To build students’ confidence in using English as a communicative tool.3. To help students improve their listening and note-taking skills through extensive lecture-listening activities.&nbsp;4. To introduce students to significant vocabulary words relevant to a wide range of academic topics.&nbsp;5. To prepare students to actively take part in discussions, teaching them the fundamental skills for agreeing and disagreeing with others’ opinions.&nbsp;", "到達目標": "1. Students will develop their academic skills.&nbsp;2. Students will become more confident and effective communicators.3. Students will strengthen their listening comprehension, note-taking and discussion skills.4. Students will acquire new vocabulary that will enhance their academic achievement.", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "1. This course will be conducted in English only and English will be the means of communication between the students and the instructor.&nbsp;&nbsp;(Students will also be expected to communicate with one another in English.)2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Students are encouraged to actively participate in class discussions, both independently and collaboratively, in order to enhance their competence and confidence in English and also to create a better learning environment for all.&nbsp;", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:Cambria,serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">Startup Week</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">】リンク：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;color:rgb(238,0,0);\"=\"roman',ser